                    "inline": [
                      {
                        "kind": "text",
                        "text": "If a is an int and less than zero, if a or p are not 1-dimensional,\nif a is an array-like of size 0, if p is not a vector of\nprobabilities, if a and p have different lengths, or if\nreplace=False and the sample size is greater than the population\nsize"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ],
